.TH "LIGHTNING-PEER-OUR-RESERVE-SUM" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-our-reserve-sum \- FEAT-2873 peer-our-reserve-sum
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-our-reserve-sum
.SH DESCRIPTION
Sum of our_reserve_msat across all peer channels (FEAT-2873).
.PP
Queries all peer channels via lightning-cli listpeerchannels and sums
our_reserve_msat for every channel.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
